      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Goals:\n • Shared understanding\n • Scales horizontally\n • Avoid single points of failure\n\nFRs:\n • Crawl website starting from\nsome set of links\n • No bound on the amount of\nlinks extracted\n • Re-fetch page after some\ntime (1 month)\n- Fairness and priority set to\nit\n\n\nNFrs\n- Scalability\n- High Availability\n- Observalibity \n- Security \n\n\nBack of evenlop\n- 1 billion links crawled every\nmonth \n- 100KB page\n- 500GB in storage space per\nmonth",
      "baseline": 93,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "cNwXaakb5pvgxEmM-zUtq",
      "originalText": "Goals:\n • Shared understanding\n • Scales horizontally\n • Avoid single points of failure\n\nFRs:\n • Crawl website starting from some set of links\n • No bound on the amount of links extracted\n • Re-fetch page after some time (1 month)\n- Fairness and priority set to it\n\n\nNFrs\n- Scalability\n- High Availability\n- Observalibity \n- Security \n\n\nBack of evenlop\n- 1 billion links crawled every month \n- 100KB page\n- 500GB in storage space per month",
      "index": "aD",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
